             was indicted for <rs id="t18330214-195-off1088" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18330214-195-off1088" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18330214-195-off1088" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
